# Current protocol
- Manual coregistration and cell by cell QC
- Using BigWarp

## Automated branch (in development)
- 2-D top-slab surface registration is solved by
  `code/dev_code/surface_registration_v2.py`
  (`get_surface_registration(s)` → JSON-cached, picks the best of
  rigid / affine / PWR 3×3 / PWR 4×4, scored as Pearson NCC of the
  warped CZ binary against the raw 488 MIP).
- See `docs/08 Automated surface registration.md` for full details
  (target choice, method definitions, validation results).
- Pia / surface fits live in `code/dev_code/surfaces_iter08.py`
